---
---

<section
  id="testimonials"
  class="relative py-20 lg:py-28 bg-white overflow-hidden"
>
  <!-- Background accents -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute -top-24 left-1/3 w-80 h-80 bg-primary-50 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-32 right-0 w-80 h-80 bg-brand-blue-purple/15 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12 lg:mb-16" data-animate>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-dark-purple mb-4">
        Trusted by Award Winning Communities
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-16 lg:space-y-20">
      <!-- Row 1: image left, two testimonials right -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <!-- Image stack -->
        <div class="relative max-w-xl mx-auto" data-animate>
          <!-- Base image -->
          <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-white bg-white">
            <img
              src="/images/equera-testimonial1.png"
              alt="Community using Equera"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Overlay image: top-right, tilted -->
          <div
            class="sm:block absolute -top-6 -right-4 max-w-[180px] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl transform rotate-12 translate-x-4"
          >
            <img
              src="/images/equera-testimonial2.png"
              alt="Equera experience on mobile"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonials -->
        <div class="space-y-8 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed" data-animate>
          <figure class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-7 shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
            <blockquote class="mb-4">
              “This is going to be game-changing for us, and also for the CBTOs”
            </blockquote>
            <figcaption class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-dark-purple">
              — Community Tourism Leader
              <div class="text-xs font-normal text-gray-500">
                (UN Best Tourism Villages award winner)
              </div>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>

          <figure class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-7 shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
            <blockquote class="mb-4">
              “A platform like Equera offers visibility, connection and shared purpose.”
            </blockquote>
            <figcaption class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-dark-purple">
              — Eco-Tourism Organization
            </figcaption>
          </figure>

          <figure class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 max-w-xl mx-auto text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <blockquote class="mb-4">
              “Finally, our village has found the right sustainability partner that understands and addresses tourism development gaps we've faced over the years”
            </blockquote>
            <figcaption class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-dark-purple">
              — Community Tourism Leader
              <div class="text-xs font-normal text-gray-500">
                (UN Best Tourism Villages award winner)
              </div>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

